            <h6>What is this site?</h6>
            <p>
                This site is primarily two things: a web development portfolio and a personal blog. However, it has an auxiliary function which naturally occurred as a byproduct of the other two goals, and has ended up informing a lot of the design choices I’ve made here: it’s also my online identity, a way for me to express my values and character to potential employers, coworkers, clients, or collaborators. Hence the buzzwords on the landing page.
